The requirements for this final project were to embody the spirit of the novel and inspire viewers to find out more.
fields.title: Italo Calvino's Cosmicomics by Sheri Prather

fields.description:
An online video promotion for Italo Calvino's novel Cosmicomics by Dennis Coveyou for a motion graphics course at DePaul University's School of Cinema & Interactive Media in Chicago. The requirements for this final project were to embody the spirit of the novel and inspire viewers to find out more. 

Thanks Scott Butwina, Joe Gondolfi, Sam Gondolfi, and Sloan Gretencord for superb acting.
fields.title: Italo Calvino's Cosmicomics by Dennis Coveyou
